snippet.title: Age of Wonders: Planetfall INVASIONS - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
In the stardust and disunity of the collapsed Star Union, an insidious new race of conquerors has come to lay claim to the galaxy. Deploy and destroy as the merciless Shakarn, a vicious race of conniving lizardmen. https://www.aow-planetfall.com/invasions
